Title: Thermo Boots Black
Description:
Thermo Boots Black - En Fant

For winter, the Enfant Thermoboots are absolutely essential. These winter boots, lined with wool, keep your little one's feet wonderfully warm during cold and rainy days. The boots are waterproof, so you don't have to worry about wet socks while jumping in puddles!

The lining of the Thermoboots is made of 90% wool and 10% polyester.

Please note that the Enfant Thermoboots run small. We recommend ordering one size larger.
